date | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 12:03 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 12:03 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776168222393,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"341b62a7\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the last known state in memory.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_m5g3m92npqrv_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"activeMinutes\": 60,\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_m5g3m92npqrv_2\",\n              \"name\": \"memory_get\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"path\": \"heartbeat-state.json\",\n                \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 430,\n            \"output\": 99,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14473,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n  