        \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Duplicate of the previous heartbeat. No action needed.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"HEARTBEAT_OK\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 248,\n            \"output\": 19,\n            \"totalTokens\": 94896,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 94629,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776167846301,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d5ea7838454abc3a300a8e527f699\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"e582cb77\",\n            \"seq\": 1133\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 11:53 UTC 14 Apr\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status to Lead) — **RESOLVED** ✅ — session cleared, delivery attempts ended\\n• cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry) — **RESOLVED** ✅ — no longer in sessions list, system cleaned up after ~83 min stuck period\\n• All previously-flagged stuck sessions now cleared\\n\\nPipeline: **HEALTHY** ✅\\n• Active sessions: 2 (both 5p cron monitors running stable)\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Blockers: None\\n\\n— Orbis 🌐\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776167856615,\n          \"provenance\": {\n            \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n            \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n            \"sourceChannel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n          },\n          \"__opencla